  "ai_usage": "Use for product changelogs / release notes. Render a vertical timeline of <article> entries, each with version, a real <time datetime>, category tags (New/Improved/Fixed) with text, and short bullets. Add a subscribe prompt. Keep heading order logical, tags text-labeled (not color-only), and animate entries in on scroll with a reduced-motion guard.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/changelog-page.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Changelog / Release Notes</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"changelog-page\",\n  \"title\": \"Changelog / Release Notes\",\n  \"summary\": \"A product changelog: a vertical timeline of releases, each with a version, date, category tags (New / Improved / Fixed), and bullet points.\",\n  \"description\": \"The 'what's new' page modern products keep — a timeline rail with dated version entries, color-coded change tags, concise bullets, and a subscribe prompt. Sticky version markers and reveal-on-scroll keep it scannable.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"saas\", \"content\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"changelog\", \"release-notes\", \"timeline\", \"updates\", \"versions\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"beginner\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers.\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"A CSS timeline (pseudo-element rail) + reveals. No libraries.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Entries are <article>s with real <time datetime>; tags include text; heading order is logical; the subscribe form is labeled. Reduced-motion safe.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"tag colors\", \"description\": \"New / Improved / Fixed\", \"default\": \"green / violet / amber\" },\n    { \"name\": \"entries\", \"description\": \"Release blocks\", \"default\": \"edit markup\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Filter by tag\", \"RSS/email subscribe\", \"Group by month\"],\n  \"related\": [\"docs-portal\", \"blog-article\", \"pricing-page\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for product changelogs / release notes. Render a vertical timeline of <article> entries, each with version, a real <time datetime>, category tags (New/Improved/Fixed) with text, and short bullets. Add a subscribe prompt. Keep heading order logical, tags text-labeled (not color-only), and animate entries in on scroll with a reduced-motion guard.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--bg:#0b0d12;--surface:#12151f;--line:#242a3b;--text:#e8ecf6;--muted:#8b93a7;--accent:#7c5cff;\n    --new:#34d399;--imp:#a78bff;--fix:#fbbf24;--r:14px;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}\n  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:\"Inter\",system-ui,sans-serif;line-height:1.7}\n  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n  .wrap{max-width:760px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.4rem}\n  nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:64px}\n  .brand{font-weight:800}.links{color:var(--muted);display:flex;gap:1.2rem;font-size:.92rem}.links a:hover{color:var(--text)}\n  header.hero{text-align:center;padding:3rem 0 1rem}\n  header.hero h1{font-size:clamp(2rem,5vw,3rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:0 0 .4rem}\n  header.hero p{color:var(--muted)}\n  .sub{display:flex;gap:.5rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:1.2rem 0 .5rem}\n  .sub input{background:var(--surface);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:10px;padding:.6rem .9rem;color:var(--text);min-width:220px}\n  .sub button{background:var(--accent);color:#fff;border:none;border-radius:10px;padding:.6rem 1.1rem;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer}\n  .timeline{position:relative;padding:2rem 0 3rem;margin-left:8px}\n  .timeline::before{content:\"\";position:absolute;left:7px;top:0;bottom:0;width:2px;background:var(--line)}\n  .entry{position:relative;padding-left:2.4rem;margin-bottom:2.6rem}\n  .entry::before{content:\"\";position:absolute;left:0;top:6px;width:16px;height:16px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent);box-shadow:0 0 0 4px var(--bg)}\n  .ver{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:.8rem;flex-wrap:wrap}\n  .ver h2{font-size:1.3rem;margin:0}.ver time{color:var(--muted);font-size:.85rem}\n  .tags{display:flex;gap:.4rem;flex-wrap:wrap;margin:.6rem 0 .4rem}\n  .tag{font-size:.72rem;font-weight:800;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;padding:.15rem .55rem;border-radius:999px}\n  .t-new{background:rgba(52,211,153,.15);color:var(--new)}.t-imp{background:rgba(167,139,255,.15);color:var(--imp)}.t-fix{background:rgba(251,191,36,.15);color:var(--fix)}\n  ul{margin:.4rem 0 0;padding-left:1.1rem;color:var(--muted)}li{margin:.25rem 0}li b{color:var(--text)}\n  button:focus-visible,input:focus-visible{outline:3px solid var(--accent);outline-offset:2px}\n  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);text-align:center;padding:2rem 0;font-size:.9rem}\n  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px);transition:opacity .5s,transform .5s ease}.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"wrap\">\n    <nav><div class=\"brand\">◆ Nimbus</div><div class=\"links\"><a href=\"#\">Docs</a><a href=\"#\">Blog</a><a href=\"#\">App ↗</a></div></nav>\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n      <h1>Changelog</h1>\n      <p>New features, improvements, and fixes — shipped continuously.</p>\n      <form class=\"sub\" onsubmit=\"event.preventDefault();this.querySelector('button').textContent='Subscribed ✓'\">\n        <input type=\"email\" placeholder=\"you@example.com\" aria-label=\"Email for updates\" required>\n        <button type=\"submit\">Get updates</button>\n      </form>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"timeline\">\n      <article class=\"entry reveal\">\n        <div class=\"ver\"><h2>v3.2</h2><time datetime=\"2026-05-28\">May 28, 2026</time></div>\n        <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag t-new\">New</span><span class=\"tag t-imp\">Improved</span></div>\n        <ul><li><b>Agents 2.0:</b> build autonomous workflows in plain language.</li><li>Search is now <b>3× faster</b> on large workspaces.</li><li>Added keyboard shortcuts for every primary action.</li></ul>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"entry reveal\">\n        <div class=\"ver\"><h2>v3.1</h2><time datetime=\"2026-05-14\">May 14, 2026</time></div>\n        <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag t-new\">New</span><span class=\"tag t-fix\">Fixed</span></div>\n        <ul><li><b>Slack integration</b> with two-way sync.</li><li>Fixed a rare data-export timeout on huge projects.</li><li>Dark mode now respects per-document overrides.</li></ul>\n      </article>\n      <article class=\"entry reveal\">\n        <div class=\"ver\"><h2>v3.0</h2><time datetime=\"2026-04-30\">Apr 30, 2026</time></div>\n        <div class=\"tags\"><span class=\"tag t-new\">New</span><span class=\"tag t-imp\">Improved</span><span class=\"tag t-fix\">Fixed</span></div>\n        <ul><li>Completely <b>redesigned editor</b> with live collaboration.</li><li>Rebuilt the API — 40% smaller payloads.</li><li>Squashed 60+ bugs from the beta.</li></ul>\n      </article>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>© <span id=\"yr\"></span> Nimbus, Inc. · Follow along on the changelog.</footer>\n  </div>\n  <script>\n    document.getElementById('yr').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();\n    var io=new IntersectionObserver(function(es){es.forEach(function(e){if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('in');io.unobserve(e.target)}})},{threshold:.15});\n    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function(el){io.observe(el)});\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
